thread.title_full: DIGIPRINT SUPPLIES évalué par guillaume blondiau

author: guillaume blondiau
title: guillaume blondiau
text: Digiprint Supplies has been my supplier for a year now. I buy all my parts from them for my Roland printer and they are great. Orders are delivered the next day and they help me on their support platform to diagnose problems or install the parts. Their staff is dedicated and they are reachable 24 hours a day. I am delivered faster from Digiprint than any supplier in the UK.
